${BOLD}bcs check$NC - AI-powered BCS compliance checking

${BOLD}Usage:$NC $SCRIPT_NAME check [OPTIONS] SCRIPT

${BOLD}Options:$NC
  -m, --model MODEL       Model alias or canonical model ID (${BOLD}sonnet$NC default)
