  Each level sets max output tokens and (on capable models) the thinking or
  reasoning budget. Anthropic thinking is auto-enabled on opus + sonnet-4-6
  and skipped silently elsewhere; OpenAI reasoning_effort is auto-enabled on
  o-series + gpt-5*; Gemini thinkingConfig is auto-enabled on the 2.5 family
  except flash-lite. Ollama ignores both.

  low         Clear violations only (4k tokens, no thinking; alias: min)
  medium      Violations and significant warnings (8k tokens, 2k thinking)
  high        All violations and warnings (24k tokens, 6k thinking)
  xhigh       Comprehensive audit with detailed reasoning (40k tokens, 12k thinking)
  max         Exhaustive line-by-line audit (64k tokens, 16k thinking)

${BOLD}Tiers & Severity:$NC
  Rules carry a ${BOLD}**Tier:**$NC field. The check command maps tier to severity:
